      "creatureType": "",
      "blurb": "",
      "publicNotes": "<h3>Conversion notes (this module)</h3><p><strong>Role:</strong> four janni slaves murdered into fungal puppetry by the wizard Innachi Naven (who learned the Arkonas' nature and was fed to Senshiir for it). They tend the hidden grotto-garden (D19) and kill all non-Arkonas on sight.</p><p><strong>Tactics:</strong> invisible on approach; open with overlapping spore clouds, then scimitars; they shrink the party's biggest threat. They pursue through the cavern but never into D24/D25 or the palace above. They fight to the death — there is nothing left in them to fear with.</p>",
