    {
      "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/spells/create-food.webp",
      "name": "Create Food",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>You create enough food to feed six Medium creatures for a day. This food is bland and unappealing, but it is nourishing. After 1 day, if no one has eaten the food, it decays and becomes inedible. Most Small creatures eat one-quarter as much as a Medium creature (one-sixteenth as much for most Tiny creatures), and most Large creatures eat 10 times as much (100 times as much for Huge creatures and so on).</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (4th)</strong> You can feed 12 Medium creatures.</p>\n<p><strong>Heightened (6th)</strong> You can feed 50 Medium creatures.</p>\n<p><strong>Heightened (8th)</strong> You can feed 200 Medium creatures.</p>"
        },
